                <h1>Can You Use Wallpaper Paste on Peel and Stick Wallpaper?</h1>
                <p>Using wallpaper paste on peel and stick wallpaper is generally not recommended. Peel and stick options are designed for easy installation and removal without additional adhesives. Applying wallpaper paste can hinder their repositionability and may damage the surface when removed. For best results, use them as intended.</p>
